videos.headline: Mills finds Wilson for 26-yard Stanford TD
videos.description: Davis Mills makes a short pass to Michael Wilson, who runs 26 yards into the end zone for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Mills finds Wilson for 26-yard Stanford TD) 2019/09/28

videos.headline: Mills connects with Parkinson for Cardinal TD
videos.description: Davis Mills finds Colby Parkinson for the three-yard touchdown to give Stanford a 14-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Mills connects with Parkinson for Cardinal TD) 2019/09/28

videos.headline: Pierce runs in for 43-yard Oregon State TD
videos.description: Artavis Pierce runs 43 yards into the end zone for an Oregon State touchdown to make it 21-14.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Pierce runs in for 43-yard Oregon State TD) 2019/09/28

videos.headline: Toner kicks game-winning field goal for Stanford
videos.description: With one second remaining, Jet Toner hits a field goal and Stanford wins 31-28.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Toner kicks game-winning field goal for Stanford) 2019/09/28
